 on February 10 at [[The New Beginning (2013)|The New Beginning]], where Okada, positioned as the face, was defeated by the stable's leader Minoru Suzuki, following interference from [[Taichi Ishikari|Taichi]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.njpw.co.jp/match/detail_result.php?e=687|title=The New Beginning|accessdate=2013-02-10|work=[[New Japan Pro-Wrestling]]|language=Japanese}}</ref> In preparation for the [[2013 New Japan Cup]], Okada announced that he had created a new submission finishing maneuver, the ''[[Professional wrestling holds#Cross-legged STF|Red Ink]]'', in order to win the tournament.<ref name=RedInk>{{cite web|url=http://www.tokyo-sports.co.jp/prores/117716/|script-title=ja:\u30aa\u30ab\u30c0\u65b0\u6280\u300c\u30ec\u30c3\u30c9\u30a4\u30f3\u30af\u300d\u3067\u5b8c\u5168\u5fa9\u6d3b\u3060|date=2013-03-10|accessdate=2013-03-10|work=[[Tokyo Sports]]|language=Japanese}}</ref> On March 11, he used the ''Red Ink'' to defeat Suzuki-gun member and [[IWGP Tag Team Champion]] [[Lance Archer]] in his first round match.<ref name=NJPW031113>{{cite web|url=http://www.njpw.co.jp/match/detail_result_game.php?e=695&c=5180|title=New Japan Cup 2013|accessdate=2013-03-11|work=[[New Japan Pro-Wrestling]]|language=Japanese}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.f4wonline.com/more/more-top-stories/118-daily-updates/30209-mon-update-notes-on-tonights-raw-who-was-flown-in-new-japan-cup-and-smith-scores-biggest-carer-win-hogan-lawsuit-impact-summerslam-tickets-dino-bravo-end-of-us-tvs-greatest-villain-nash-does-tv-shoot-marathon-of-movies-from-past-wrsetler-|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130313173409/http://www.f4wonline.com/more/more-top-stories/118-daily-updates/30209-mon-update-notes-on-tonights-raw-who-was-flown-in-new-japan-cup-and-smith-scores-biggest-carer-win-hogan-lawsuit-impact-summerslam-tickets-dino-bravo-end-of-us-tvs-greatest-villain-nash-does-tv-shoot-marathon-of-movies-from-past-wrsetler-|title=Mon. update: Notes on tonight's Raw, Who was flown in, New