itt vs. Tanahashi, NWA Title defended, Benjamin, Hoyt, Shelley, more|date=2013-06-22|accessdate=2013-06-22|work=Pro Wrestling Torch}}</ref> On July 20, Okada made his third successful title defense against [[IWGP Junior Heavyweight Champion]] [[Prince Devitt]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.njpw.co.jp/match/detail_result.php?e=738|script-title=ja:\u5409\u91ce\u5bb6Presents Kizuna Road 2013|accessdate=2013-07-20|work=[[New Japan Pro-Wrestling]]|language=Japanese}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nikkansports.com/battle/news/f-bt-tp0-20130721-1160750.html|script-title=ja:\u738b\u8005\u30aa\u30ab\u30c0\u3001\uff13\u5ea6\u76ee\u9632\u885b\u6210\u529f\uff0f\u65b0\u65e5\u672c|date=2013-07-21|accessdate=2013-07-20|work=[[Nikkan Sports]]|language=Japanese}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://sportsnavi.yahoo.co.jp/sports/fight/headlines/article/20130721-00000000-spnavi|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131002175549/http://sportsnavi.yahoo.co.jp/sports/fight/headlines/article/20130721-00000000-spnavi|script-title=ja:\uff36\uff13\u6210\u529f\u306e\uff29\uff37\uff27\uff30\u738b\u8005\u30fb\u30aa\u30ab\u30c0\u304c\uff27\uff11\u9023\u8987\u5ba3\u8a00\uff1d\u65b0\u65e5\u672c\u30d7\u30ed\u30ec\u30b9|archivedate=2013-10-02|date=2013-07-21|accessdate=2013-07-20|work=Sports Navi|publisher=[[Yahoo!]]|language=Japanese}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wrestleview.com/misc-news/42741-7-20-njpw-results-akita-japan-devitt-vs-okada|title=7/20 NJPW iPPV Results: Akita, Japan (Devitt vs. Okada)|last=Namako|first=Jason|date=2013-07-20|accessdate=2013-07-20|work=Wrestleview}}</ref> From August 1 to 11, Okada took part in the [[2013 G1 Climax]],<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.njpw.co.jp/news/detail.php?nid=9857 |script-title=ja:\u30d6\u300eG1 Climax 23\u300f\u51fa\u5834\u30e1\u30f3\u30d0\u30fc\u767a\u8868!! \u98ef\u4f0f\u5e78\u592a\u3001\u77f3\u4e95\u667a\u5b8f\u304c\u521d\u51fa\u5834!! \u67f4\u7530\u52dd\u983c\u304c9\u5e74\u3076\u308a\u30a8\u30f3\u30c8\u30ea\u30fc!! |date=2013-07-0